(4. ELIGIBILITY CRITERIA) Tj T*
(================================================================================) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(NOTE: Eligibility shall be evaluated on the basis of the documents) Tj T*
(submitted by the bidder in Cover 1 \(Technical Bid\). Any bid not meeting) Tj T*
(the mandatory criteria below shall be REJECTED without proceeding to Cover 2.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Table 1   Mandatory Eligibility Criteria) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Sl. | Criterion                | Requirement) Tj T*
(----|--------------------------|----------------------------------------------) Tj T*
( 1  | Annual Turnover          | Average Annual Turnover not less than) Tj T*
(    |                          | Rs. 25.00 Crore per year, from civil / building) Tj T*
(    |                          | construction works, in each of the last 3) Tj T*
(    |                          | financial years \(FY 2023-24, 2024-25, 2025-26\)) Tj T*
(----|--------------------------|----------------------------------------------) Tj T*
( 2  | Technical Experience     | Successfully completed at least 2 \(two\) similar) Tj T*
(    |                          | institutional or government building construction) Tj T*
(    |                          | works, each of value not less than Rs. 5.00 Crore,) Tj T*
(    |                          | in the last 7 \(seven\) years) Tj T*
(----|--------------------------|----------------------------------------------) Tj T*
( 3  | ISO Certification        | Valid ISO 9001:2015 certification \(current\)) Tj T*
(----|--------------------------|----------------------------------------------) Tj T*
( 4  | CPWD Registration        | Valid CPWD registration   Class I or Special) Tj T*
(    |                          | Class Civil Contractor \(or SS/S class with) Tj T*
(    |                          | appropriate financial limit endorsement\)) Tj T*
(----|--------------------------|----------------------------------------------) Tj T*
( 5  | Net Worth                | Net Worth not less than Rs. 5.00 Crore as on) Tj T*
