(The following amendment is hereby made to the Notice Inviting Tender) Tj T*
(issued on 03 June 2026:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Item 1   Eligibility Criteria Table 1, Sl. No. 1: Annual Turnover) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(  Original requirement:) Tj T*
(    Average Annual Turnover not less than Rs. 25.00 Crore per year from) Tj T*
(    civil / building construction works in each of the last 3 financial years.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(  Amended requirement:) Tj T*
(    Average Annual Turnover not less than Rs. 50.00 Crore per year from) Tj T*
(    civil / building construction works in each of the last 3 financial years.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(  Reason: Estimated project cost revised upward by approximately 18% due) Tj T*
(  to site investigation report showing adverse soil conditions requiring) Tj T*
(  deeper foundations. The Annual Turnover threshold has been revised) Tj T*
(  proportionally to ensure adequate financial capacity.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Item 2   Completion Period) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(  Original: 18 months) Tj T*
(  Amended: 22 months \(revised following revised scope from site investigation\)) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(All other terms and conditions of the original NIT dated 03 June 2026) Tj T*
(remain unchanged.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Bidders who have already downloaded the original tender document must note) Tj T*
(this amendment. The Corrigendum is also available on the CPWD e-Tender) Tj T*
(portal under the same NIT reference.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
